{
  "title": "Delicate Resinous Chinese Foie Gras Buddha Jumps Over Wall",
  "description": "A romantic Chinese dish featuring foie gras, presented in a Buddha Jumps Over Wall form, with a resinous and glassy jelly texture, served in a molcajete vessel.",
